The paper deals with natural language understanding and automatic question generation, which are core topics in the field of computational linguistics (cs.CL). The proposed approach involves using language models and supervised training, which are also common techniques in artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and machine learning (cs.LG). The paper also mentions the use of monolingual text and question answering, which are relevant to neural networks (cs.NE) and information retrieval (cs.IR).
